HOME FOR CHRISTMAS forwardly placed three wide through the first turn, tracked the leader in closest aim just off the inside, came under coaxing at the five-sixteenths, swung four wide into upper stretch and weakened. CURLY GIRL grew keen pulling under restraint just after the start along the inside and brushed the temporary rail near seven and a half furlongs to run, tracked along the inside coming under coaxing at the five-sixteenths, took the inside route into upper stretch and tired.
